********  WARNING  ************

  ALL SNOOPS ARE LOGGED.  spying on a player for no better reason 
than just to do it will not be tolerated by the admin of this mud.
Use this command to help fiond bugs and see what exactly the player 
did etc.  but in no way use it to spy on players.

